(126, '1', 'sc_admin/product/create', 'POST', '127.0.0.1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/110.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"kind\":\"0\",\"descriptions\":{\"en\":{\"name\":\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - \\u0110\\u1ed3ng H\\u1ed3 Nam - \\u0110i\\u1ec7n T\\u1eed - K\\u00ednh Nh\\u1ef1a - Size M\\u1eb7t 45mm - B\\u1ea3o H\\u00e0nh 5 N\\u0103m - Ch\\u00ednh H\\u00e3ng 100%\",\"keyword\":\"\\u0110\\u1ed3ng H\\u1ed3 Nam\",\"description\":\"\\u0110\\u1ed3ng H\\u1ed3 Nam\",\"content\":\"<p>B\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang t&igrave;m ki\\u1ebfm m\\u1ed9t m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u1ed3 \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed m\\u1eb7t vu&ocirc;ng, v\\u1edbi thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf kh\\u1ecfe kho\\u1eafn, s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu nhi\\u1ec1u ti\\u1ec7n &iacute;ch v&agrave; m\\u1ee9c gi&aacute; r\\u1ebb? Th&igrave; s\\u1ef1 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ho&agrave;n h\\u1ea3o kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 kh&ocirc;ng nh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u1ed3&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD<\\/strong>&nbsp;(Hay Casio AE-1200WHD-1A). \\u0110&acirc;y l&agrave; d&ograve;ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u Casio n\\u1ed5i ti\\u1ebfng, v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng h\\u1eefu &iacute;ch v&agrave; kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ch\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi. H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\\\"235780294\\\" match=\\\"ch\\u00fa\\\">ch&uacute;<\\/em>ng t&ocirc;i t&igrave;m hi\\u1ec3u d&ograve;ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m&nbsp;<strong>\\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u1ed3 Casio<\\/strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y \\u1edf nh\\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin sau.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - \\u1ea2nh 1\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.watchstore.vn\\/uploads\\/editor\\/AE1200WHD-1-1627025521621.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - \\u1ea2nh 1\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"gioi-thieu-ve-mau-dong-ho-casio-ae-1200whd\\\">Gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u1ec1 m\\u1eabu \\