m thng hiu u din ra&nbsp;<strong><em loopnumber=\"788402178\" match=\"100% \">100%&nbsp;</em>ti Trung Quc</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 2\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/2-1675328748899.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>ng h Reef Tiger ca Trung Quc</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng cn c tr&ecirc;n &acirc;y cho thy nhn nh thng hiu ng h Reef Tiger ca Trung Quc rt c&oacute; kh nng rt ln. Nhng cho n nay, v ph&iacute;a i din h&atilde;ng Reef Tiger vn cha c&oacute; hi &aacute;p c th, x&aacute;c thc th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"danh-gia-chat-luong-dong-ho-reef-tiger\">&aacute;nh gi&aacute; cht lng ng h Reef Tiger</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"thiet-ke\">Thit k</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 3\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/3-1675328762571.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 3\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Reef Tiger thit k v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng tinh t, sc n&eacute;t</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>V ngo&agrave;i ca Reef Tiger kh&ocirc;ng thua k&eacute;m bt c thng hiu&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-nhat-ban-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">Nht</a></strong>&nbsp;hay&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-thuy-sy-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">Thy S</a></strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;o. Nhng sn phm ca Reef Tiger c thit k ht sc&nbsp;<strong>t m v&agrave; tinh xo</strong>&nbsp;kh&ocirc;ng ch&ecirc; v&agrave;o &acirc;u c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Reef Tiger i theo thit k thanh lch, sang trng nhng cng ht sc tr trung, thi thng. Bi thit k p mt m&agrave; Reef Tiger c rt nhiu ngi y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch v&agrave; la chn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 4\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/4-1675328778191.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 4\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>ng h Reef Tiger hp vi rt nhiu la tui</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Reef Tiger s dng cho rt nhiu ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng vi nhiu  tui t&nbsp;<strong>sinh vi&ecirc;n, hc sinh n ngi i l&agrave;m, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n vn ph&ograve;ng, doanh nh&acirc;n</strong>,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th t tin khi eo ng h Reef Tiger i l&agrave;m, i tic, i chi,... Nh thit k mi m, a dng, h&atilde;ng &atilde; thu v doanh thu rt ln mi nm vi s lng sn phm b&aacute;n ra ht sc ln.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"bo-may\">B m&aacute;y</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c sn phm ca Reef Tiger c trang b 2 d&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ch&iacute;nh &oacute; l&agrave; &ldquo;<strong><em>b m&aacute;y ni a Trung v&agrave; b m&aacute;y nhp khu Nht Bn</em></strong>&rdquo;. C&aacute;c d&ograve;ng m&aacute;y ni a Trung u c sn xut v&agrave; t cht lng rt tt. Ngo&agrave;i ra, Reef Tiger cng thng mua b m&aacute;y ca thng hiu&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/blogs/news/dong-ho-seiko-cua-nuoc-nao--nhung-san-pham-lam-nen-ten-tuoi-seiko-325\" target=\"_blank\">Seiko</a></strong>&nbsp; trang b cho c&aacute;c sn phm ca m&igrave;nh. Bi vy khi s dng, ngi d&ugrave;ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m v cht lng sn phm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 5\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/5-1675328811802.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 5\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Reef Tiger s dng b m&aacute;y ni a Trung hoc ca Nht</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"tinh-nang\">T&iacute;nh nng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c sn phm ca thng hiu Reef Tiger u c trang b y  c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng nhm mang n tri nghim ngi d&ugrave;ng tt nht. Nhng t&iacute;nh nng thng c thy trong ng h Reef Tiger &oacute; l&agrave; &ldquo;<strong>lch ng&agrave;y, th, ng h 24h,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/blogs/news/chronograph-la-gi--cach-nhan-biet-dong-ho-chronograph-chuan-nhat-56\" target=\"_blank\">chronograph</a>, tachymeter (o tc  di chuyn)&quot;</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"chat-lieu\">Cht liu</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 6\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/4-1675328831366.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 6\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Reef Tiger c trang b cht liu bn b, cht lng</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng thua k&eacute;m c&aacute;c sn phm ca Nht, Thy S, c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng ng h Reef Tiger cng c trang b nhng vt liu ht sc cht lng, bn b nh &ldquo;<em>th&eacute;p kh&ocirc;ng g (khung v&agrave; v ng h), da cao cp (d&acirc;y eo), mineral crystal v&agrave; sapphire (mt k&iacute;nh)</em>&rdquo;. Vi nhng cht liu tr&ecirc;n<em loopnumber=\"788402178\" match=\"m bo\">&nbsp;m bo&nbsp;</em>ng h t  bn b tt nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"dong-ho-reef-tiger-co-gia-bao-nhieu\">ng h Reef Tiger c&oacute; gi&aacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute; rt nhiu thc mc kh&ocirc;ng bit &ldquo;<em>ng h Reef Tiger c&oacute; gi&aacute; bao nhi&ecirc;u</em>? C&oacute; rt nhiu ngi nhm ln rng &quot;<em>ng h sn xut ti Trung Quc n&ecirc;n chc c&oacute; gi&aacute; r</em>&rdquo;. Nhng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng phi vy. Tuy c sn xut v&agrave; tin n l&agrave; &ldquo;<strong>thng hiu Trung Quc</strong>&rdquo; nhng nhng sn phm Reef Tiger u c ch t&aacute;c b&agrave;i bn theo&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"788402178\" match=\"c\">c&ocirc;</em>ng ngh hin i &aacute;p ng c c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chun cht lng kht khe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bi th cho n&ecirc;n tuy kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; thng hiu ng h qu&aacute; xa x nhng Reef Tiger cng l&agrave; 1 thng hiu ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng. Th n&ecirc;n gi&aacute; b&aacute;n ca Reef Tiger lu&ocirc;n giao ng t&nbsp;<strong>3 triu - hn 4 triu ng</strong>&nbsp;mt sn phm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 7\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/6-1675328850644.jpg\" title=\"ng h Reef Tiger ca nc no? c hay Trung Quc? - nh 7\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Mc gi&aacute;