('963b22df-8bcd-475e-9c6a-eb6bb7469711', 'en', 'About', NULL, NULL, '<p>Mt trong nhng im n ca s an t&acirc;m khi mua h&agrave;ng, kh&ocirc;ng th kh&ocirc;ng nhc ti WatchStore &ndash; h thng ph&acirc;n phi ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng vi u &atilde;i cc tt ti Vit Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"nhuc-nhoi-van-nan-dong-ho-gia-tran-lan\">Nhc nhi vn nn ng h gi tr&agrave;n lan</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ng&agrave;y nay,&nbsp;<strong>ng h eo tay</strong>&nbsp;tr th&agrave;nh mt m&oacute;n  c&aacute; nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng th thiu ca mi ngi. D&ugrave; nam hay n, d&ugrave; c&aacute; t&iacute;nh hay thanh lch, d&ugrave; nng ng hay du d&agrave;ng, d&ugrave; ln tui hay tr tui th&igrave; u cn s hu mt chic ng h, kh&ocirc;ng ch  x&aacute;c nh thi gian, n&oacute; c&ograve;n l&agrave; mt m&oacute;n ph kin gi&uacute;p truyn ti th&ocirc;ng ip t &ldquo;c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i&rdquo; ca mi ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/4342800_Tissot_t_0331-1628432094730.webp\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nTht kh&oacute; c&oacute; th m xu c&aacute;c thng hiu ng h tr&ecirc;n th trng Vit Nam n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng v&agrave; th trng th gii n&oacute;i chung. Ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; a dng s la chn v kiu d&aacute;ng cng nh gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh ca sn phm, ch t 199.000 ti 399.000 bn cng c&oacute; th mua c mt chic ng h v&agrave; cng c&oacute; loi gi&aacute; tr s hu l&ecirc;n ti 8 con s.<br />\r\nCh cn mt lnh search t kho&aacute;&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>tim ng h</strong>&nbsp;gn &acirc;y hay n&ecirc;n mua ng h  &acirc;u l&agrave; Google s tr v cho bn h&agrave;ng trm kt qu t&igrave;m kim.<br />\r\nNhan nhn c&aacute;c website b&aacute;n ng h v&agrave; k&ecirc;nh facebook qung c&aacute;o rm r rng m&igrave;nh l&agrave; a&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h uy t&iacute;n</strong>,<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"cam kt\">&nbsp;cam kt&nbsp;</em>h&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng gi&aacute; cc r nhng kh&ocirc;ng th show ra c y  cn c  chng minh iu &oacute;. Ch&iacute;nh s tr&agrave;n lan v c&aacute;c ca tim ng h v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h gi&aacute; r</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y khin ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng d ri v&agrave;o trng th&aacute;i hoang mang mi khi c&oacute; &yacute; nh sm cho m&igrave;nh mt chic&nbsp;<strong>ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</strong>.<br />\r\n<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">Trc&nbsp;</em>vn nn h&agrave;ng gi, h&agrave;ng nh&aacute;i ang ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng tng cao. Thm ch&iacute;,  tinh vi ca h&agrave;ng fake mt thng kh&oacute; c&oacute; th ph&acirc;n nh c, ch c&oacute; th nhn bit th&ocirc;ng qua qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh thm nh bi th chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n cao, th&igrave; vic t&igrave;m hiu  mua mt chic ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng l&agrave; iu kh&oacute; hn bao gi ht. Vy t&igrave;m  &acirc;u mt&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h uy t&iacute;n gi&aacute; r</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n th trng hin nay l&agrave; iu m&agrave; rt nhiu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng quan t&acirc;m t&igrave;m kim.<br />\r\n tr&aacute;nh bn th&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng b ri v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh trng tr&ecirc;n, ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng cn tnh t&aacute;o v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng th&aacute;i khi la chn ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n. C&ugrave;ng tham kho mt s kinh nghim  ph&acirc;n bit ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng v&agrave; ng h fake, cng nh c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; &aacute;nh gi&aacute; shop ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-phan-biet-dong-ho-chinh-hang\">C&aacute;ch ph&acirc;n bit ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-phan-mat-so-va-mat-kinh\">Kim tra phn mt s v&agrave; mt k&iacute;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mi mt thng hiu, mt d&ograve;ng ng h s c&oacute; nhng c im rt ri&ecirc;ng bit  nhn bit. V&iacute; d nh vi d&ograve;ng ng h Thu S,  nhng chic ng h ch&iacute;nh hiu lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; d&ograve;ng ch &ldquo;Swiss made&rdquo; cc k sc so, c in cc nh b&ecirc;n di s 6. D&ograve;ng ch ngay ngn,nm c&acirc;n xng vi s 6,c&oacute;  cao bng nhau v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng b nho&egrave;. iu n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ngha rng c c&oacute; ch &ldquo;Swiss Made&rdquo; th&igrave; l&agrave; ng h chun ca Thu S nhng nu &atilde; l&agrave; ng h Thu S th&igrave; &acirc;y l&agrave; iu bt buc phi c&oacute;.<br />\r\nPhn mt ng h c ch t&aacute;c vi  ho&agrave;n ho gn nh tuyt i, men tr&aacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng b gn, m&agrave;u sc ng u, s&aacute;ng b&oacute;ng,  d&agrave;y nh nhau. To&agrave;n b c&aacute;c chi tit tr&ecirc;n mt nh con s u rt sc n&eacute;t, c&acirc;n xng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/phan-biet-tissot-5-1629171789888.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nNu shop b&aacute;n ng h &oacute; qung c&aacute;o vi bn rng phn mt k&iacute;nh ng h l&agrave; k&iacute;nh Sapphire th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th kim tra bng c&aacute;ch nh mt git nc l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n b mt k&iacute;nh,<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"sau \">&nbsp;sau &oacute;&nbsp;</em>nghi&ecirc;ng ng h. Nu nc t li mt v tr&iacute; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng b chy t&igrave; &oacute; l&agrave; chun k&iacute;nh Sapphire, c&ograve;n nu nc b chy i th&igrave; c&oacute; ch l&agrave; k&iacute;nh thng hoc l&agrave; k&iacute;nh cng lc.<br />\r\nKim tra xem phn kim ca ng h c&oacute; to th&agrave;nh h&igrave;nh tam gi&aacute;c c&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng<br />\r\nH&atilde;y quan s&aacute;t k to h&igrave;nh ca kim ng h, 2 ng v&aacute;t s lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; mt tam gi&aacute;c c&acirc;n. Phn ng r&atilde;nh dc ca kim tht sc n&eacute;t, i t nh xung di.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-phan-day-deo\">Kim tra phn d&acirc;y eo</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;y gi cht mt u ca d&acirc;y eo<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"sau \">&nbsp;sau &oacute;&nbsp;</em>lc qua lc li,  c&aacute;c ng h h&agrave;ng hiu cao cp ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng th&igrave; phn d&acirc;y s rt chc chn, s&oacute;ng u, nu c m v&agrave;ng th&igrave; nc m lu&ocirc;n u m&agrave;u nhau. C&ograve;n nu l&agrave; h&agrave;ng k&eacute;m cht lng th&igrave; d&acirc;y s lng lo, kh&ocirc;ng chc chn, phn nc m kh&ocirc;ng c u m&agrave;u</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/nhung-cach-kiem-tra-day-deo-dong-ho-bang-da-that-gia-de-dang-chuan-xac-1629171852029.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\ni vi d&acirc;y kim loi, c&oacute; th kim tra bng c&aacute;ch gp mt d&acirc;y vi nhau, nu c&aacute;c mt li&ecirc;n tip lin nhau v&agrave; c&oacute;  m ging nhau th&igrave; c&oacute; l&agrave; d&acirc;y eo ca ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng. Phn mt trong ca d&acirc;y cng phi b&oacute;ng l&aacute;ng mn ch kh&ocirc;ng b nh&aacute;m, b kh&ocirc;ng u nh h&agrave;ng gi.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"chu-y-phan-am-thanh-khi-hoat-dong-cua-dong-ho\"><em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"ch\">Ch&uacute;</em>&nbsp;&yacute; phn &acirc;m thanh khi hot ng ca ng h</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh s t m khi ch t&aacute;c, c&aacute;c loi ng h m&aacute;y c ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng s hot ng &ecirc;m &aacute;i, kim gi&acirc;y chy mt m&agrave;, kh&ocirc;ng ph&aacute;t ra ting ng. Cng tng t nh m&aacute;y Quartz s chy mt ch kh&ocirc;ng b git.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-cac-dau-hieu-duoc-khac-dap-tren-dong-ho\">Kim tra c&aacute;c du hiu c khc, dp tr&ecirc;n ng h</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Phn mt trong ca ng h s c&oacute; c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng k thut c bn nh cht liu ca v m&aacute;y, cht liu ca k&iacute;nh, cht liu ca d&acirc;y eo,  chu nc, s seri, loi m&aacute;y...Tt c nhng th&ocirc;ng tin n&agrave;y u c khc in ng u, c&acirc;n i, sc n&eacute;t, c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng font ch. Nu ph&aacute;t hin th&ocirc;ng s sai th&igrave; bn n&ecirc;n t&igrave;m n ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n kh&aacute;c  mua.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-phan-tem-phieu-bao-hanh\">Kim tra phn tem, phiu bo h&agrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ph kin i k&egrave;m ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng bao gi cng c&oacute;  b gm hp ng, th bo h&agrave;nh ca h&atilde;ng, hng dn s dng&hellip;mt s&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n</strong>&nbsp;c&ograve;n c&oacute; c&aacute;c t&uacute;i x&aacute;ch ca h&agrave;ng. Tt c c&aacute;c ph kin i k&egrave;m u c sn xut rt sc so, tr&ugrave;ng khp th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n ng h.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/news/chinh-sach-bao-hanh-watchstore.jpg\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/news/chinh-sach-bao-hanh-watchstore.jpg\" title=\"\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c im khc dp  v b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i cng phi tht sc n&eacute;t, tinh t, ng u, kh&ocirc;ng b loang hay nho&egrave;. Th&ocirc;ng thng biu tng thng hiu s c dp khc  phn n&uacute;m hoc hoc phn kho&aacute;  d&acirc;y. Nhng sn phm fake ph kin i k&egrave;m thng nh&igrave;n rt di, ng n&eacute;t th&ocirc;, kh&ocirc;ng ng u, c&oacute; tim b&aacute;n ng h c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; hoc kh&ocirc;ng  ph kin</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-trong-luong\">Kim tra trng lng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Do c l&agrave;m t nhng vt liu cao cp v&agrave; c&oacute;  bn cao n&ecirc;n nhng chic ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng thng s c&oacute; trng lng nng hn so vi c&aacute;c loi ng h l&agrave;m nh&aacute;i li.<br />\r\nC&aacute;c bn cng phi lu &yacute; rng mi thng hiu ng h s c&oacute; nhng c im, c&aacute;ch ph&acirc;n bit tht gi kh&aacute;c nhau. Kh&ocirc;ng th ch cn c v&agrave;o c&aacute;c c im cm quan  la chn, tt nht bn n&ecirc;n t&igrave;m n c&aacute;c&nbsp;<strong>a ch mua ng h uy t&iacute;n</strong>, c&aacute;c i l&yacute; c u quyn ch&iacute;nh thc  chn mt gi v&agrave;ng nh&eacute;.<br />\r\n<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">Trc&nbsp;</em>khi quyt nh la chn&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n</strong>&nbsp; sm cho m&igrave;nh mt chic ng h hiu ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng th&igrave; bn cn t&igrave;m biu k c&agrave;ng, kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n hp tp. H&atilde;y t&igrave;m hiu th&ocirc;ng tin&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">trc&nbsp;</em> tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c&nbsp;<strong>trang web b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n ti Vit Nam</strong>, c&aacute;c group  xem &acirc;u l&agrave; shop ng h c nhiu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao nht nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-thong-tin-ve-gia-ca\">Kim tra th&ocirc;ng tin v gi&aacute; c</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>a phn c&aacute;c&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng ng h gi&aacute; r ti H&agrave; Ni</strong>&nbsp;n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng v&agrave; tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc n&oacute;i chung, thng ch&agrave;o gi&aacute; ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng vi mc gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh rt r, ch bng &frac12;, thm ch&iacute; 1/10 so vi gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m yt.<br />\r\nNu bn ang t&igrave;m hiu v mt chic ng h Seiko c&oacute; gi&aacute; ni&ecirc;m yt hn 10 triu ng, m&agrave; c&oacute; ni ang b&aacute;n ch 200, 300 ng&agrave;n, th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi suy ngh, &oacute;&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"chc chn \">chc chn&nbsp;</em>l&agrave; h&agrave;ng fake!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"cac-dac-diem-cua-mot-cua-hang-ban-dong-ho-uy-tin\">C&aacute;c c im ca mt ca h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"lua-chon-cua-hang-dong-ho-uy-tin-co-quy-mo-lon\">La chn ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n c&oacute; quy m&ocirc; ln</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">Trc&nbsp;</em>khi quyt nh&nbsp;<strong>mua ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng  &acirc;u</strong>&nbsp;bn n&ecirc;n tham kho th&ocirc;ng tin top ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n H&agrave; Ni hoc&nbsp;<strong>top ca h&agrave;ng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng ti tpHCM</strong>&nbsp; chn lc ra nhng&nbsp;<strong>ni b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n nh</strong>t, c&oacute; quy m&ocirc; ln vi c&aacute;c c im nh c&oacute; h thng showroom tr&ecirc;n c nc, c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng u c&oacute; a ch kinh doanh r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, y  bin t&ecirc;n&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/cua-hang-dong-ho-chinh-hang-watchstore-1629172297293.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nKh&ocirc;ng phi t nhi&ecirc;n&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>ng t&ocirc;i khuy&ecirc;n bn &ldquo;nh&igrave;n mt m&agrave; bt h&igrave;nh dong&rdquo;, nhng ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n s kh&ocirc;ng ngi show mi th mnh cho ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng thy,  thu h&uacute;t kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng h s lu&ocirc;n c gng x&acirc;y dng showroom ca m&igrave;nh tht ni bt, sang trng. Ch kh&ocirc;ng cn phi chui li, n m&igrave;nh nh c&aacute;c i tng la o.<br />\r\nVic nm trong tay c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin a ch&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"chc chn \">chc chn&nbsp;</em>cng s gi&uacute;p bn thun li trong vic phn &aacute;nh, gii quyt c&aacute;c vn  ph&aacute;t sinh&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"sau \">sau&nbsp;</em>mua b&aacute;n nh bo h&agrave;nh, bo dng.<br />\r\nMt s ngi thng quan nim rng: La chn mua h&agrave;ng ti c&aacute;c tim ng h gn nht s gi&uacute;p bn d d&agrave;ng kim tra v quy m&ocirc; cng nh thun tin trong vic bo h&agrave;nh sn phm. iu n&agrave;y cng hp l&yacute;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, thay v&igrave; chn c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng ng h gn nht m&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo h&agrave;nh cng nh u &atilde;i kh&ocirc;ng nhiu, bn s b &ldquo;thit th&ograve;i&rdquo; kh&aacute; ln. Li khuy&ecirc;n l&agrave; bn h&atilde;y t&igrave;m hiu v&agrave; la chn c&aacute;c ca tim ng h c&oacute; c s r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo h&agrave;nh v&agrave; chm s&oacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng hp l&yacute;  y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m mua h&agrave;ng.<br />\r\nH thng showroom ca WatchStore tri d&agrave;i tr&ecirc;n c nc, c&oacute; mt ti H&agrave; Ni, &agrave; Nng, H Ch&iacute; Minh. Sn s&agrave;ng phc v nhu cu tri nghim sn phm ca qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"chinh-sach-bao-hanh-dong-ho-chinh-hang\">Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo h&agrave;nh ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n lu&ocirc;n cung cp ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo h&agrave;nh ti&ecirc;u chun cho sn phm v&agrave; c&oacute; giy chng nhn i l&yacute; u quyn ca c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng ang b&agrave;y b&aacute;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ca h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n WatchStore lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; y  giy t chng nhn i l&yacute; u quyn v&agrave; em n cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch bo h&agrave;nh an t&acirc;m nht l&ecirc;n ti 5 nm.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"full-phu-kien-di-kem\">Full ph kin i k&egrave;m</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi mua sn phm ti c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng, ngo&agrave;i ng h bn s nhn c c&aacute;c ph kin i k&egrave;m bao gm hp, s hng dn, th bo h&agrave;nh, t&uacute;i ca ch&iacute;nh nh&agrave; sn xut.<br />\r\nWatchStore<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"cam kt\">&nbsp;cam kt&nbsp;</em>mi chic ng h b&aacute;n ra u<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"m bo\">&nbsp;m bo&nbsp;</em>y  ph kin ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng. Bao thm nh sn phm  bt c &acirc;u, nu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ph&aacute;t hin h&agrave;ng fake s ho&agrave;n tin gp 20 ln gi&aacute; tr sn phm.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"tai-sao-nen-lua-chon-he-thong-dong-ho-chinh-hang-watchstore\">Ti sao n&ecirc;n la chn h thng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng WatchStore?</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"su-menh--phuong-cham-hoat-dong\">S mnh &amp; phng ch&acirc;m hot ng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>L&agrave; mt trong nhng chui ca h&agrave;ng ph&acirc;n phi ng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng uy t&iacute;n bc nht tr&ecirc;n th trng ti Vit Nam, WatchStore l&agrave; a ch mua sm tin tng ca rt nhiu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, c bit l&agrave; nhng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng am m&ecirc; su tp ng h.<br />\r\nc th&agrave;nh lp vi s mnh &ldquo;chung tay y l&ugrave;i h&agrave;ng fake&rdquo;, h thng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng WatchStore ang n lc g&oacute;p phn ph&aacute;t trin mt cng ng s dng ng h THT, mang ti nhng sn phm cht lng cao vi nhng u &atilde;i hp dn, l&agrave; mt trong c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n c nhiu ngi la chn.<br />\r\nKh&ocirc;ng ch l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng ng h H&agrave; Ni</strong>&nbsp;c ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng a chung, WatchStore &atilde; m rng th&ecirc;m 2 chi nh&aacute;nh, tr th&agrave;nh shop ng h uy t&iacute;n TPHCM, &agrave; Nng v&agrave; hng ti mc ti&ecirc;u ph&aacute;t trin rng khp c&aacute;c tnh th&agrave;nh.<br />\r\nTr&ecirc;n con ng n lc em ti cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cht lng sn phm v&agrave; cht lng dch v ng cp nht, WatchStore &atilde; kh&ocirc;ng ngng thay i, n&acirc;ng cao cht lng i ng chuy&ecirc;n vi&ecirc;n, a dng s lng sn phm, n&acirc;ng cp c s h tng ca m&igrave;nh, tr th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>shop b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc,</strong>&nbsp;phc v nhu cu ca c kh&aacute;ch trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i nc.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"chinh-sach-hau-mai\">Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch hu m&atilde;i</h3>\r\n\r\n<p> bo v ti a quyn li kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cng nh  kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n khi mua sm, s dng sn phm, WatchStore &atilde; x&acirc;y dng ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch hu m&atilde;i v&agrave; bo h&agrave;nh uy t&iacute;n c&oacute; 1-0-2 vi c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chun nh:<br />\r\nTt c sn phm u l&agrave; h&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng c nhp h&agrave;ng trc tip t c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&acirc;n phi ng h ln.<br />\r\n<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"100% \">100%&nbsp;</em>h&agrave;ng mi, fullbox, y  ph kin k&egrave;m theo ca nh&agrave; sn xut.<br />\r\nMc gi&aacute; cc k u &atilde;i c&ugrave;ng vi nhiu chng tr&igrave;nh khuyn m&atilde;i hp dn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"che-do-bao-hanh-len-toi-5-nam\">Ch  bo h&agrave;nh l&ecirc;n ti 5 nm.</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Min ph&iacute; 1 i 1 trong v&ograve;ng 6 th&aacute;ng i vi li t nh&agrave; sn xut.<br />\r\nMin ph&iacute; vn chuyn to&agrave;n quc, c kim tra h&agrave;ng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">trc&nbsp;</em>khi thanh to&aacute;n v&agrave; k&yacute; nhn.<br />\r\ni ng t vn chuy&ecirc;n nghip, sn s&agrave;ng h tr gii &aacute;p mi thc mc nhanh ch&oacute;ng, tn t&acirc;m.<br />\r\nHot ng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin vi ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; quyt t&acirc;m y l&ugrave;i h&agrave;ng fake, WatchStore s l&agrave; ca h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n ng h uy t&iacute;n bn n&ecirc;n la chn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"cac-thuong-hieu-dong-ho-phan-phoi-chinh-hang-tai-watchstore\">C&aacute;c thng hiu ng h ph&acirc;n phi ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng ti WatchStore</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dong-ho-seiko\"><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-seiko-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Seiko</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;&Ocirc;ng tr&ugrave;m&rdquo; ng h Nht Bn vi lch s gn 150 nm h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t trin. Th m&agrave; Seiko mang li cho bn l&agrave; cht lng v&agrave; s bn b vt thi gian.<br />\r\nC&ugrave;ng vi s ci tin v&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"c\">c&ocirc;</em>ng ngh, s ho&agrave;n thin v mu m&atilde;, cng nh s khng nh v gi&aacute; tr thng hiu, ng h Seiko &atilde; cho ra mt nhiu d&ograve;ng ng h phc v nhiu nhu cu v&agrave; ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c ngi d&ugrave;ng kh&aacute;c nhau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"seiko srpd59k1, ng h seiko chnh hng, ng h nam, my c automatic, hardlex crystal, dy kim loi, chng nc 10atm, sku/upc/mpn: 4954628232144 - nh 1\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/images/seiko-SRPD59K1-2.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nC&aacute;c d&ograve;ng sn phm Seiko l&agrave;m n&ecirc;n t&ecirc;n tui v&agrave; &aacute;ng k n nht hin nay nh: Seiko 5 automatic, Seiko Prospex, Seiko Presage&hellip; v&agrave; im nhn &ldquo;s&aacute;ng ch&oacute;i&rdquo; &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; Grand Seiko - d&ograve;ng sn phm nh cao vi s ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c gn nh tuyt i, s&aacute;nh ngang vi c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng ng h h&agrave;ng u Thy S.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dong-ho-orient\"><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-orient-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Orient</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Orient Watch l&agrave; &ldquo;con&rdquo; ca tp o&agrave;n Seiko Holding v&agrave; c triu ngi d&ugrave;ng a chung. Vi thit k a dng, ph&ugrave; hp vi mi phong c&aacute;ch, nguy&ecirc;n liu ng cp v&agrave; mc gi&aacute; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng hp l&yacute;, ng h Orient ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng khng nh v tr&iacute; vng chc ca m&igrave;nh trong cng ng nhng ngi am m&ecirc; ng h.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Orient chnh hng\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/images/SAK00002S0-5.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nC&aacute;c d&ograve;ng sn phm ng h Orient c ngi d&ugrave;ng a th&iacute;ch nht hin nay nh: Orient SK, Orient Bambino, Orient Sun and Moon, Orient Diver&hellip; Trong &oacute;, b su tp Orient Star l&agrave; s t ph&aacute; ngon mc v cht lng, t&iacute;nh nng cng nh gi&aacute; tr sn phm.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dong-ho-citizen\"><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-citizen-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Citizen</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Ng&ocirc;i sao&rdquo; t&acirc;n binh kh&ocirc;ng ngng ph&aacute;t trin, l&agrave; mt trong 3 nh&agrave; sn xut ng h ln nht ti Nht Bn, s hu mc doanh thu khng l h&agrave;ng nm, Citizen ang tng bc mang t&ecirc;n tui ca m&igrave;nh chng minh tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th gii v cht lng cng nh s ng cp trong tng sn phm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Citizen chnh hng\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/images/CITIZEN-NJ0120-81E-2.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nC&aacute;c d&ograve;ng ng h Citizen ph bin gm c&oacute; Citizen m&aacute;y quartz pin, Citizen automatic, &aacute;ng<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"ch\">&nbsp;ch&uacute;&nbsp;</em>&yacute; nht &oacute; l&agrave; d&ograve;ng Eco Drive c quyn c ph&aacute;t minh bi ch&iacute;nh c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ch t&aacute;c ng h ca&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"c\">c&ocirc;</em>ng ty Citizen.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dong-ho-casio\"><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-casio-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Casio</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ging c&aacute;c thng hiu ng h truyn thng, Casio tp trung ph&aacute;t trin v&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"c\">c&ocirc;</em>ng ngh v&agrave; t&iacute;nh nng ca ng h.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Casio Chnh Hng\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/images/CASIO-AE-1200WHD-1AVDF-2.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nSo v mc gi&aacute;, ng h Casio nm  ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c trung cp. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c mu ng h Casio c rt nhiu ngi d&ugrave;ng a chung, c bit l&agrave; gii tr, bi nhng t&iacute;nh nng hu &iacute;ch v&agrave; hin i m&agrave; n&oacute; mang li.<br />\r\nC&aacute;c d&ograve;ng ng h Casio ph bin: Casio MTP/ LTP, Casio Edifice, Casio G-Shock v&agrave; Baby-G...</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dong-ho-tissot\"><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-tissot-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Tissot</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Tissot ra i t nm 1853 v&agrave; &atilde; th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"c\">c&ocirc;</em>ng chinh phc tr&aacute;i tim ca nhng ngi am m&ecirc; ng h. S hu thit k sang trng, s dng c&aacute;c cht liu cao cp, c&ugrave;ng b m&aacute;y ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng Thy S vi  ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c tuyt vi, ng h Tissot 1853 vn lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; nim y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch v&agrave; s t h&agrave;o trong cng ng nhng ngi am m&ecirc;&nbsp;<strong>ng h eo tay</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ng h Tissot chnh hng\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/images/dong-ho-tissot-t006.407.11.033.00_2-ims.jpg\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nNu bn ang t&igrave;m mua cho m&igrave;nh mt chic ng h th thao hay mt chic dress watch sang trng,<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"m bo\">&nbsp;m bo&nbsp;</em>ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng 100%, WatchStore l&agrave; 1 la chn kh&ocirc;ng th b qua.</p>');
INSERT INTO `sc_shop_page_description` (`page_id`, `lang`, `title`, `keyword`, `description`, `content`) VALUES
('963b22df-8bcd-475e-9c6a-eb6bb7469711', 'vi', 'Gii thiu', NULL, NULL, '<p>Mt trong nhng im n ca s an t&acirc;m khi mua h&agrave;ng, kh&ocirc;ng th kh&ocirc;ng nhc ti WatchStore &ndash; h thng ph&acirc;n phi ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng vi u &atilde;i cc tt ti Vit Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"nhuc-nhoi-van-nan-dong-ho-gia-tran-lan\">Nhc nhi vn nn ng h gi tr&agrave;n lan</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ng&agrave;y nay,&nbsp;<strong>ng h eo tay</strong>&nbsp;tr th&agrave;nh mt m&oacute;n  c&aacute; nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng th thiu ca mi ngi. D&ugrave; nam hay n, d&ugrave; c&aacute; t&iacute;nh hay thanh lch, d&ugrave; nng ng hay du d&agrave;ng, d&ugrave; ln tui hay tr tui th&igrave; u cn s hu mt chic ng h, kh&ocirc;ng ch  x&aacute;c nh thi gian, n&oacute; c&ograve;n l&agrave; mt m&oacute;n ph kin gi&uacute;p truyn ti th&ocirc;ng ip t &ldquo;c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i&rdquo; ca mi ngi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" data-display=\"inline\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/4342800_Tissot_t_0331-1628432094730.webp\" title=\"\" /><br />\r\nTht kh&oacute; c&oacute; th m xu c&aacute;c thng hiu ng h tr&ecirc;n th trng Vit Nam n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng v&agrave; th trng th gii n&oacute;i chung. Ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; a dng s la chn v kiu d&aacute;ng cng nh gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh ca sn phm, ch t 199.000 ti 399.000 bn cng c&oacute; th mua c mt chic ng h v&agrave; cng c&oacute; loi gi&aacute; tr s hu l&ecirc;n ti 8 con s.<br />\r\nCh cn mt lnh search t kho&aacute;&nbsp;<strong>ca h&agrave;ng ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>tim ng h</strong>&nbsp;gn &acirc;y hay n&ecirc;n mua ng h  &acirc;u l&agrave; Google s tr v cho bn h&agrave;ng trm kt qu t&igrave;m kim.<br />\r\nNhan nhn c&aacute;c website b&aacute;n ng h v&agrave; k&ecirc;nh facebook qung c&aacute;o rm r rng m&igrave;nh l&agrave; a&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h uy t&iacute;n</strong>,<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"cam kt\">&nbsp;cam kt&nbsp;</em>h&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng gi&aacute; cc r nhng kh&ocirc;ng th show ra c y  cn c  chng minh iu &oacute;. Ch&iacute;nh s tr&agrave;n lan v c&aacute;c ca tim ng h v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h gi&aacute; r</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y khin ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng d ri v&agrave;o trng th&aacute;i hoang mang mi khi c&oacute; &yacute; nh sm cho m&igrave;nh mt chic&nbsp;<strong>ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</strong>.<br />\r\n<em loopnumber=\"732664833\" match=\"trc \">Trc&nbsp;</em>vn nn h&agrave;ng gi, h&agrave;ng nh&aacute;i ang ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng tng cao. Thm ch&iacute;,  tinh vi ca h&agrave;ng fake mt thng kh&oacute; c&oacute; th ph&acirc;n nh c, ch c&oacute; th nhn bit th&ocirc;ng qua qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh thm nh bi th chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n cao, th&igrave; vic t&igrave;m hiu  mua mt chic ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng l&agrave; iu kh&oacute; hn bao gi ht. Vy t&igrave;m  &acirc;u mt&nbsp;<strong>shop ng h uy t&iacute;n gi&aacute; r</strong>&nbsp;tr&ecirc;n th trng hin nay l&agrave; iu m&agrave; rt nhiu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng quan t&acirc;m t&igrave;m kim.<br />\r\n tr&aacute;nh bn th&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng b ri v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh trng tr&ecirc;n, ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng cn tnh t&aacute;o v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng th&aacute;i khi la chn ca h&agrave;ng ng h uy t&iacute;n. C&ugrave;ng tham kho mt s kinh nghim  ph&acirc;n bit ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng v&agrave; ng h fake, cng nh c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; &aacute;nh gi&aacute; shop ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"cach-phan-biet-dong-ho-chinh-hang\">C&aacute;ch ph&acirc;n bit ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kiem-tra-phan-mat-so-va-mat-kinh\">Kim tra phn mt s v&agrave; mt k&iacute;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mi mt thng hiu, mt d&ograve;ng ng h s c&oacute; nhng c im rt ri&ecirc;ng bit  nhn bit. V&iacute; d nh vi d&ograve;ng ng h Thu S,  nhng chic ng h ch&iacute;nh hiu lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; d&ograve;ng ch &ldquo;Swiss made&rdquo; cc k sc so, c in cc nh b&ecirc;n di s 6. D&ograve;ng ch ngay ngn,nm c&acirc;n xng vi s 6,c&oacute;  ca