('98ad0c1c-41be-4880-b0eb-d3939de98046', 'en', 'Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - ng H Nam - in T - Knh Nha - Size Mt 45mm', 'ng H Nam', 'ng H Nam', '<p>Bn ang t&igrave;m kim mt mu ng h in t mt vu&ocirc;ng, vi thit k khe khon, s hu nhiu tin &iacute;ch v&agrave; mc gi&aacute; r? Th&igrave; s la chn ho&agrave;n ho kh&ocirc;ng th kh&ocirc;ng nhc n &oacute; l&agrave; ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;(Hay Casio AE-1200WHD-1A). &acirc;y l&agrave; d&ograve;ng sn phm n t thng hiu Casio ni ting, vi nhiu t&iacute;nh nng hu &iacute;ch v&agrave; kh nng chng thm nc tuyt vi. H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"235780294\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>ng t&ocirc;i t&igrave;m hiu d&ograve;ng sn phm&nbsp;<strong>ng h Casio</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y  nhng th&ocirc;ng tin sau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 1\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/AE1200WHD-1-1627025521621.jpg\" title=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 1\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"gioi-thieu-ve-mau-dong-ho-casio-ae-1200whd\">Gii thiu v mu ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE-1200WHD</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>i vi th h 9x th&igrave; mu ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;&atilde; tr th&agrave;nh k&yacute; c. &acirc;y l&agrave; mu ng h hi sinh t thit k&nbsp;<strong>Casio F91</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; b v b&aacute;t gi&aacute;c rt huyn thoi trong qu&aacute; kh. Kh&aacute;c vi phi&ecirc;n bn c th&igrave;&nbsp;<strong>AE1200</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; k&iacute;ch thc ln hn, mc  ho&agrave;n thin tt hn, c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng cng u vit hn v&agrave; tin &iacute;ch ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n vt tri. c bit, &acirc;y cng l&agrave; mu thit k c bit n l&agrave; cc k bn b.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tng th mu&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-nam-casio-dien-tu-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h in t Casio</a>&nbsp;n&agrave;y kh&aacute; va vn v&agrave; ph&ugrave; hp vi c tay ca ngi &Aacute; &ocirc;ng. Nhng ng thi cng th hin c s nam t&iacute;nh vn c&oacute; ca m&igrave;nh. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute; th&igrave; gi&aacute; tr thm<em loopnumber=\"235780294\" match=\"m\">&nbsp;m&nbsp;</em>ca mu ng h n&agrave;y c&ograve;n c&oacute; s kt hp n gin ca c&aacute;c m&agrave;u sc. Vy n&ecirc;n &acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; sn phm c&oacute; doanh s b&aacute;n ra cc khng tr&ecirc;n th trng hin nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 2\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/AE1200WHD-3-1627025543073.jpg\" title=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE 1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; thit k nam t&iacute;nh</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"cac-tinh-nang-noi-bat-cua-dong-ho-casio-ae1200whd\">C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng ni bt ca ng h Casio AE1200WHD</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-nam-casio-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h nam Casio</a>&nbsp;gi&aacute; r, nu x&eacute;t v t&iacute;nh nng, rt him mu ng h n&agrave;o c&oacute; gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh hp l&yacute; v&agrave; s hu t&iacute;nh nng vt tri nh&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE-1200WHD-1A</strong>. ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;s hu c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng cc k hu &iacute;ch&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"235780294\" match=\"sau \">sau&nbsp;</em>&acirc;y:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h m ngc l&agrave; chc nng n tng ca mu ng h n&agrave;y. C&oacute; th m ngc thi gian bt u do bn ch nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&egrave;n LED gi&uacute;p chiu s&aacute;ng thun tin xem gi ban &ecirc;m hoc trong kh&ocirc;ng gian ti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhiu m&uacute;i gi (4 th&agrave;nh ph kh&aacute;c nhau)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chc nng gi th gii gm c&oacute; 31 m&uacute;i gi v&agrave; 48 th&agrave;nh ph kh&aacute;c nhau. Hin th ti c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh ph ln v&agrave; c&aacute;c khu vc kh&aacute;c nhau tr&ecirc;n th gii.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;n hiu thi gian gi h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y</p>\r\n\r\n<p>nh dng khung gi 12/24</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bt/tt &acirc;m c&oacute; th nhn n&uacute;t</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gi hin h&agrave;nh ht sc th&ocirc;ng dng nh: gi, ph&uacute;t, gi&acirc;y, th, ng&agrave;y, th&aacute;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h bm gi ht sc tin &iacute;ch, o ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c thi gian tr&ocirc;i qua ch vi mt ln bm (thun tin cho c&aacute;c hot ng th thao)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phn lch ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n t ng cho ph&eacute;p t ng sp xp th&aacute;ng c&oacute;  d&agrave;i kh&aacute;c nhau, bao gm c nm nhun (n nm 2099)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu ng h n&agrave;y c&oacute; chc nng b&aacute;o thc, gi&uacute;p cho bn c&oacute; th h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y b&aacute;o thc nh v&agrave;o c&agrave;i t cho ng h.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"tai-sao-khach-hang-nen-so-huu-dong-ho-casio-ae1200whd\">Ti sao kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng n&ecirc;n s hu ng h Casio AE1200whd</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"thiet-ke-an-tuong-va-khoa-hoc\">Thit k n tng v&agrave; khoa hc</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&acirc;y c coi l&agrave; mu ng h c&oacute; thit th&ocirc;ng minh c nhiu ngi a chung. Gi a phng lu&ocirc;n hin th  hng 10 gi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Analog ca ng h. M&uacute;i gi tr&ecirc;n bn  th gii c hin th ph&iacute;a b&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Digital. Phn tr&ecirc;n c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh nh hin th tt c c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng &aacute;p dng tr&ecirc;n ng h. C&aacute;c ph&iacute;m iu chnh chc nng bao gm: Light, Mode, Search v&agrave; Adjust</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 3\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/49897734_1975956769178649_7173216385051394048_n-1627025644327.jpg\" title=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 3\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"tuoi-tho-cao-va-gia-ca-phai-chang\">Tui th cao v&agrave; gi&aacute; c phi chng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; tui th i c&ugrave;ng nm th&aacute;ng. Hn na nu c mua  nhng a ch ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng th&igrave; gi&aacute; c s lu&ocirc;n<em loopnumber=\"235780294\" match=\"m bo\">&nbsp;m bo&nbsp;</em>chun x&aacute;c v&agrave; hp l&yacute; nht. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng bt c i tng n&agrave;o cng c&oacute; th s hu mu ng h thi thng n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"kha-nang-chong-nuoc-tot\">Kh nng chng nc tt</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Casio AE1200</strong>&nbsp;c trang b kh nng chng nc l&ecirc;n n 10ATM. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt trong nhng con s chng nc l&yacute; tng ca ng h eo tay hin nay. Nh vy m&agrave; ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th thoi m&aacute;i khi s dng  chi th thao, c&oacute; hot ng di nc nh bi li, lt v&aacute;n... C&ograve;n i vi c&aacute;c hot ng c&aacute; nh&acirc;n nh tm ra th&igrave; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng h b nh hng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"su-dung-chat-lieu-sieu-ben\">S dng cht liu si&ecirc;u bn</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Phn d&acirc;y eo kim loi c l&agrave;m t th&eacute;p kh&ocirc;ng g, c&oacute;  bn tt, kh nng chng thm cao. ng thi mt k&iacute;nh bng nha nguy&ecirc;n cht c&oacute; kh nng chng xc, chng va p cc tt bo v an to&agrave;n b m&aacute;y b&ecirc;n trong.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"de-dang-thay-doi-phong-cach\">D d&agrave;ng thay i phong c&aacute;ch</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"235780294\" match=\"sau \">sau&nbsp;</em>1 thi gian s dng, bn &atilde; nh&agrave;m ch&aacute;n vi phn d&acirc;y kim loi v&agrave; mun i mi chic ng h ca m&igrave;nh tr n&ecirc;n l mt hn? Th&igrave; vi&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE-1200WHD</strong>, bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th thay i vi d&acirc;y da  mu ng h ca m&igrave;nh c kho&aacute;c l&ecirc;n tm &aacute;o mi, tr n&ecirc;n v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng c&aacute; t&iacute;nh, nng ng v&agrave; th thao.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 4\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/AE1200WHD-5-1627026009038.jpg\" title=\"Casio AE-1200WHD-1AVDF - nh 4\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu sn phm ng h&nbsp;<strong>Casio AE1200WHD</strong>&nbsp;kh&ocirc;ng ch g&acirc;y st th trng Vit Nam, m&agrave; c&oacute; to c sc hp dn tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; hin nay.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"dia-chi-uy-tin-va-chat-luong-de-mua-dong-ho-casio-ae1200whd\">a ch uy t&iacute;n v&agrave; cht lng  mua ng h Casio AE1200WHD</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>WatchStore.vn ch&iacute;nh l&agrav