store.vn/uploads/editor/SK-1626661205904.jpg\" title=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>n nm 2015, sn phm bt ng c Orient &ldquo;hi sinh&rdquo; vi thit k gn nh l&agrave; tng t bn 1970. Gn nht l&agrave; nm 2019, d&ograve;ng&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-orient-sk-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Orient SK</a></strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y li tip tc c tung ra th trng. Nh&agrave; sn xut vn gi nguy&ecirc;n c kiu d&aacute;ng c in nhng c&aacute;c chi tit &atilde; c ci tin  ph&ugrave; hp vi thi i. Ngay t khi &ldquo;t&aacute;i xut&rdquo;, sn phm n&agrave;y &atilde; g&acirc;y c ting vang cc ln trong gii ng h.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"thiet-ke-cua-dong-ho-sk-mat-lua-ban-2019\">Thit k ca ng h SK mt la bn 2019</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>So vi&nbsp;<strong>ng h SK mt la 2015</strong>&nbsp;th&igrave; bn 2019 vn c thit k nguy&ecirc;n form c. Mt s vn c gi nguy&ecirc;n v&agrave;nh benzel c&oacute; th xoay  t&iacute;nh gi. im kh&aacute;c bit m&agrave; bn c&oacute; th nhn thy r&otilde; r&agrave;ng ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; phn n&uacute;m bm  hng 2h b loi b. Thay v&agrave;o &oacute; t&iacute;nh nng chnh lch th c Orient t&iacute;ch hp ngay v&agrave;o trong n&uacute;m xoay  g&oacute;c 3h. iu n&agrave;y gi&uacute;p cho phi&ecirc;n bn mi nht n&agrave;y c&oacute; gim gi&aacute;c gn hn bn c rt nhiu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> bn ng h c, to&agrave;n b phn mt s u c ph mt lp m&agrave;u  c&aacute;nh sen. Nhng vi bn&nbsp;<strong>SK 2019</strong>, m&agrave;u  tp trung v&agrave;o phn ch&iacute;nh gia v&agrave; tn dn ra 2 b&ecirc;n. iu n&agrave;y gi&uacute;p cho ngi d&ugrave;ng nh&igrave;n ng h c&oacute; chiu s&acirc;u hn nh hiu ng th gi&aacute;c. Phn kh&oacute;a ca sn phm cng c i t kh&oacute;a m&oacute;c th&agrave;nh bm. Nh &oacute; bn c&oacute; th y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m hn khi s dng v&agrave; thao t&aacute;c th&aacute;o ng h cng d d&agrave;ng hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 3\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/RA-AA0B02R19B-3-1626660841887.