jpg\" title=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 3\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>c bit l&agrave; b m&aacute;y ca ng h&nbsp;<strong>Orient SK mt la 2019</strong>&nbsp;c trang b Caliber F6922. C&ugrave;ng vi &oacute; sn phm c&oacute; 22 ch&acirc;n k&iacute;nh, 40 gi t&iacute;ch c&oacute;t v&agrave; 2 t&iacute;nh nng c bit l&agrave; Hacking-Stop v&agrave; Hand-Winding. Nh &oacute; ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng thao t&aacute;c cng nh iu chnh theo &yacute; mun ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"dac-diem-noi-bat-cua-dong-ho-orient-sk-2019\">c im ni bt ca ng h Orient SK 2019</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ng h Orient SK 2019</strong>&nbsp;&atilde; chim trn c cm t&igrave;nh ca nhiu ngi bi n&oacute; em li rt nhiu c im ni bt. C th:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sn phm kiu d&aacute;ng tr&ograve;n vi ng k&iacute;nh mt 42mm c l&agrave;m t cht liu k&iacute;nh kho&aacute;ng. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt trong nhng vt liu kh&ocirc;ng ch cng c&aacute;p m&agrave; c&ograve;n c&oacute; kh nng chng va p cao v&agrave; d d&agrave;ng &aacute;nh b&oacute;ng li khi b try xc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 4\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/RA-AA0B02R19B-2-min-1626660732906.jpg\" title=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 4\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>B mt ng  c trang b lch ng&agrave;y, b&ecirc;n cnh &oacute; c&ograve;n c ph th&ecirc;m 1 lp d quang n&ecirc;n bn c&oacute; th xem gi k c trong m&ocirc;i trng thiu s&aacute;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V v&agrave; d&acirc;y ng  c ch t&aacute;c t cht liu th&eacute;p kh&ocirc;ng g gi cho ng h lu&ocirc;n c s&aacute;ng b&oacute;ng. Do &oacute; bn c&oacute; th thoi m&aacute;i s dng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng s b n m&ograve;n hay hoen g&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"208094815\" match=\"sau \">sau&nbsp;</em>thi gian d&agrave;i s dng. Np&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"208094815\" match=\"sau \">sau&nbsp;</em>c&oacute; th xoay vn v&agrave; c in logo Orient rt p mt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D&acirc;y eo c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y chnh va vn vi c tay ca ngi d&ugrave;ng  to cm gi&aacute;c thoi m&aacute;i nht.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chic ng h n&agrave;y c&ograve;n c trang b th&ecirc;m kh nng chng nc 5ATM. Bn c&oacute; th thoi m&aacute;i i di ma, ra tay, ra mt m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi lo lng b thm nc hay h hng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"dia-chi-mua-dong-ho-sk-mat-lua-uy-tin\">a ch mua ng h SK mt la uy t&iacute;n</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin nay tr&ecirc;n th trng c&oacute; rt nhiu a ch cung cp nhng sn phm&nbsp;<strong>SK mt la</strong>. Nhng kh&ocirc;ng phi ch n&agrave;o cng cung cp cho bn ng h ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng, cht lng. Nu nh bn vn ang bn khon cha bit ch n&agrave;o uy t&iacute;n th&igrave; h&atilde;y n vi&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/\" target=\"_blank\">WatchStore.vn</a></strong>. Ti ca h&agrave;ng, bn c&oacute; th ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m bi to&agrave;n b sn phm ca&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"208094815\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>ng t&ocirc;i u c nhp khu ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 5\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/CH-min-1626661672189.jpg\" title=\"Orient SK RA-AA0B02R19B - nh 5\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n t vn v&agrave; h tr mt c&aacute;ch chi tit v c&aacute;c mu ng h. T &oacute; gi&uacute;p bn la chn c sn phm ph&ugrave; hp nht vi phong c&aacute;ch ca m&igrave;nh. Ngo&agrave;i ra ch  bo h&agrave;nh ca&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"208094815\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>ng t&ocirc;i cng l&ecirc;n n 5 nm cho mi sn phm. Bt c khi n&agrave;o ng h c&oacute; vn , i ng k thut s kim tra v&agrave; h tr bn trong ng&agrave;y.</p>');
