 &aacute;p ng c y&ecirc;u cu t nhiu ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;ng ng h Orient c &aacute;nh gi&aacute; l&agrave; h&atilde;ng ng h  ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c b&igrave;nh d&acirc;n nhng cht lng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"218528339\" match=\"chc chn \">chc chn&nbsp;</em>kh&ocirc;ng h tm thng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"218528339\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>t n&agrave;o. V&agrave; khi c&oacute; mt ti Vit Nam, nhng chic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.watchstore.vn/collections/dong-ho-nam-orient-chinh-hang\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Orient nam</a>, m&agrave; c th l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>ng h Orient RA-AR0001S10B</strong>&nbsp;tr th&agrave;nh la chn y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch ca nhiu ngi. L&yacute; do l&agrave; g&igrave; bn xem ngay c&ugrave;ng&nbsp;<em loopnumber=\"218528339\" match=\"ch\">ch&uacute;</em>ng t&ocirc;i nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Orient RA-AR0001S10B - nh 2\" src=\"https://cdn.watchstore.vn/uploads/editor/RA-AR0001S10B-1-1652092215326.jpg\" title=\"Orient RA-AR0001S10B - nh 2\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"thiet-ke-an-tuong-cua-orient-ra-ar0001s10b\">Thit k n tng ca Orient RA-AR0001S10B</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ln u cm chic&nbsp;<strong>ng h Orient RA-AR0001S10B</strong>, n tng u ti&ecirc;n bn cm nhn thy s l&agrave; kiu d&aacute;ng kho khon v&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng mnh m, n tng. Mt ng h c thit k l c, c th  &acirc;y l&agrave; gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; th chi&ecirc;m ngng to&agrave;n b qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh hot ng ca b m&aacute;y b&ecirc;n trong.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phong c&aacute;ch thit k l c cng Open Heart c &aacute;nh gi&aacute; l&agrave; thit k xut hin  nhng d&ograve;ng ng h t tin v&agrave; sang trng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c bit,&nbsp;<strong>ng h Orient RA-AR0001S10B</strong>&nbsp;gn nh ph&ugrave; hp vi mi k&iacute;ch c c tay ca ngi Ch&acirc;u &Aacute; n&oacute;i chung v&agrave; Vit Nam n&oacute;i ri&ecirc;ng. Kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; to cng kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; nh, ng k&iacute;nh mt s, b d&agrave;y mt s ln lt l&agrave; 40.8 mm v&agrave; 11 mm.  